phrases: Kojuro will look after the castle.

why is he sending the priestess he is been hiding back to Izumo?

I suppose someone interested in the popular foreign deities,
like Buddha or Kannon, would not know what I am talking about.

I will acquire it and turn this world upside down.

Do not run off on your own!
I will call you if something happens.

Isanami, you are so good at that.
You really are a great dancer.
I am sure you will become Izumo's best dancer.
I told you not to go off on your own.
Saizo, why do not you go look somewhere else?

and would be here to greet me.

I would like to live a quiet life in the other world.
What is that supposed to mean?
Hey, I think we are here.

Now, if you will hand it over.

Leave the older one to me.

If you must interfere with my job,
just like our meeting at Ueda Castle,
